snippet: The students were accused of attacking a woman on a beach filled with spring-break revelers who apparently did nothing to stop it, the authorities said.
abstract: Troy University students Delonte Martistee and Ryan Austin Calhoun are arrested and charged for sexually assaulting 19-year-old woman on Panama City Beach, Fla, over spring break.
lead_paragraph: The students were accused of attacking a woman on a beach filled with spring-break revelers who apparently did nothing to stop it, the authorities said.

headline.main: 2 Alabama College Students Charged in Spring Break Sexual Assault on Florida Beach
headline.print_headline: 2 Charged in Spring Break Sexual Assault on Florida Beach
